docs.text: About David David Finster is a technical editor at Vultr.com . Find him at GitHub , Stack Overflow , and Twitter . “When you are a Bear of Very Little Brain, and you Think of Things, you find sometimes that a Thing which seemed very Thingish inside you is quite different when it gets out into the open and has other people looking at it.” —Winnie the Pooh
